      "12_hygiene_mini_routine": "12. Hygiene Mini Routine",
      "ages_3_8_3": "Ages 3–8",
      "this_is_useful_for_children_who_resist_teeth": "This is useful for children who resist teeth, hair, face washing, or hand washing. The routine should be short and concrete, with small choices inside the non-negotiable task.",
      "toilet_4": "Toilet",
