      "naeyc_s": "NAEYC’s",
      "developmentally_appropriate_practice_position_statement": "Developmentally Appropriate Practice position statement",
      "is_a_good_reference_for_keeping_expectations_realistic": "is a good reference for keeping expectations realistic, strengths-based and play-based. It is written for educators, but the principles translate well to parents: children need active engagement, meaningful participation, warm relationships, and expectations that match their development.",
      "play_based_learning_and_playful_parent_child_practice": "Play-based learning and playful parent-child practice.",
      "for_the_playful_side_of_this_handbook_see": "For the playful side of this handbook, see",
